">要你活下去</span>，這個天涯海角都令人心魂寄繫的小墟。"},{"pid":"6af4716af06998bc4f51ae8166f906e96b1954e6","tid":2086662,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49de5e490dfb2fa87dbfd775ede040d2bc65e655","tid":2086662,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:28:54.000Z","msg":"離别是為了重聚，大動若靜，大善若水，明天只是另一日，香港不死，只<span style=\"color: red;\">要你活下去</span>，這個天涯海角都令人心魂寄繫的小墟。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"保存有用之軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b041744b473baca37d536604e6c8757513152f1","tid":2086662,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6175dab2dfaf613c1247ab89bb0f04e44f402eee","tid":2086662,"uid":304845,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:29:43.000Z","msg":"估唔到2020年7月仲見到熱狗式屌票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc11fd3c06e05a134bc05c53833716575c1fc33","tid":2086662,"uid":304845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"192b59c228e6813fba8567dce3616a24e213aed9","tid":2086662,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c2d5ee73310dcf30ec912fef083f167d548d609","tid":2086662,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3b00264dc1912b362761224018a523d407cb40e1","tid":2086662,"uid":97944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6175dab2dfaf613c1247ab89bb0f04e44f402eee","tid":2086662,"uid":304845,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:07:53.000Z","msg":"19又可能樂觀咗少少既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"做順民都係be water"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"做黑警都係be water<br />\nIf you can&rsquo;t beat them, join them"},{"pid":"03c9721975977302609234c47ec82ce83a40368b","tid":2086662,"uid":84781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4993c5a683499b86ec287b99e1e6c473e5e4e92","tid":2086662,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:38:23.000Z","msg":"手足，大家聽日見，準備好道具比國際傳媒影啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F0yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=5ef83c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3a1a46de4a0267ff545fce85fc3b5baff1f1bd50","tid":2086662,"uid":160506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b55f6dd570effc66dec9456f3b9f63a22750a7","tid":2086662,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ff67935138c67a343c8a0dd0bab3c8c10b871e4c","tid":2086662,"uid":325039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"19左膠論調"},{"pid":"d73d455333ac1fef6cb0fa08f709ad52f04520d8","tid":2086662,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候到我地守護番正義女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"}]}